dct_title_s: Map of the Upper portion of the Tuscarawas River Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Tuscarawas River Basin (Upper portion)
dct_description_sm: Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"
Scale bar lower left corner of map.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the upper Tuscarawas River and Chippewa Creek Basins and quality of underground water.
